      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MY WEE LASS (6) missed the frame latest when eighth at this track (16.19) but was a winner four back in the best time of the program. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Should bounce back. BIG DEL (7) settled down midfield and held his position to the line when finishing 4th (16.07) at this track. Goes well out of this box with a win and four minor placings. Can figure in the finish. MISS TWIX (1) turned in a plain effort last time when seventh at Gosford over 388m behind Laurie's Rupee (23.37) in a Grade 5. The form out of her last race has been franked. Bold showing expected. KODA MULWEE (4) has a solid strike rate at this track and distance.",
